{"tid":1969072,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳美國擬另設新組織取代世衛 下周或公佈制裁行動","createTime":"2020-04-12T07:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T16:07:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5777d8d537426f77ab734dd6adeff28988b45d04","tid":1969072,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"傳美國擬另設新組織取代世衛 下周或公佈制裁行動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1245016/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%82%B3%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E5%8F%A6%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%B0%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B-%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%88%96%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1245016%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%258F%25A6%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BD%2588%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=2e554c2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1245016%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%258F%25A6%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BD%2588%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595&h=2f5352fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1245016/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%82%B3%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E5%8F%A6%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%B0%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B-%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%88%96%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎肆虐全球，美國成為重災區之一。美國總統特朗普早前批評世界衛生組織（WHO）以中國為中心，並透露下周會決定是否向WHO停止提供資金。有美國媒體稱特朗普的幕僚正討論更多制裁WHO的行動，包括另設機構取而代之。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國Politico網站昨日引述消息人士指，政府官員已在草擬文件，一旦作出決定後，便會宣布暫停美國向WHO以及泛美衛生組織（Pan American Health Organization）的資助。這份草擬文件會同時告知國務院、美國國際開發總署（USAID）等政府機關官員嘗試將資金轉給現有的替代組織。<br />\n<br />\n有部分幕僚建議以聯合國愛滋防治計劃（UNAIDS）為基礎建立取代WHO的機構。</span></strong>聯合國愛滋防治計畫成立於1990年代中期，目的在防治愛滋病，當時也是因為對世衛組織處理愛滋疫情的方式普遍不滿而成立。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Politico又引述兩名消息人士，指美國國務院和國際開發署很多官員都支持改革WHO的想法，以及對整個聯合國進行更廣泛的改革，當中許多人在對中國政策上亦屬強硬派。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nWHO總幹事譚德塞曾反駁特朗普有關世衛「以中國為中心」的指控，指要停止將疫情「政治化」。特朗普反指譚德塞的做法才是政治化，並威脅暫停提供資金。"},{"pid":"e707e7f20b129b3b1d013911db8c907a7ec89e21","tid":1969072,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"之前日本，最近英國先捐錢，即刻乜都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a6e1d5f543ecdbfd860f07340d177be2503fd7","tid":1969072,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"今次真係睇下拋唔拋到WHO<br />\n美國應該唔係真心想另起爐灶，一搞就要兩邊鬥搶人，歐洲班屎忽鬼肯定又乘機講條件，到時仲肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46a26361104eea6acc888eff19730778d9f21ca","tid":1969072,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f1a79c4907302fc7deb1f557df18d2e1a87f5d","tid":1969072,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T10:4